id: pm-c97q
title: Docs index missing EXTENSION_AUTHOR_CONTRACTS + MIGRATION_CLI_SIMPLIFICATION links; migration note predates --pm-path
description: "docs/README.md Documentation Map (:31-45) and Read Path do not link docs/EXTENSION_AUTHOR_CONTRACTS.md (only reachable via EXTENSIONS.md:15) or docs/MIGRATION_CLI_SIMPLIFICATION.md (only reachable via CLAUDE_CODE_PLUGIN.md:162) — broken progressive disclosure for package authors and automation maintainers. Also docs/MIGRATION_CLI_SIMPLIFICATION.md:20-27,54 documents resolvePmRoot precedence as 'explicit --path' and recommends 'pass --path explicitly' without mentioning that --pm-path is now the preferred explicit flag and that explicit --path pointing at a project root is redirected to .agents/pm (PR#146, pm-ryik); CONFIGURATION.md:7-8,86-90 documents the current contract. Fix: add both pages to the docs map and add a one-line --pm-path update to the migration note."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 3
